Hilary and Jackie;;83;;88;;R;;Iris Du Pré (Celia Imrie) inspires a love of music -- and a healthy rivalry -- in her daughters, Hilary (Rachel Griffiths) and Jackie (Emily Watson). Cellist Jackie outshines her flutist sister when her skillful playing lands her in the international spotlight. Meanwhile, Hilary builds a quiet but happy family life. When Jackie buckles under mounting pressures in the high-stress world of elite classical musicians, she turns to Hilary for help, and may put her sister's love to the test.;;Biography,Drama;;Anand Tucker;;1998;;Emily Watson,Rachel Griffiths,James Frain,David Morrissey,Charles Dance,Celia Imrie,Rupert Penry-Jones,Bill Paterson,Auriol Evans,Keeley Flanders,Nyree Dawn Porter,Vernon Dobtcheff,Anand Tucker,Hilary du Pré,Piers du Pré,Frank Cottrell Boyce,Guy East,Ruth Jackson,Nicolas Kent,Andy Paterson,Nigel Sinclair,Iain Jones,Barrington Pheloung,David Johnson,Martin Walsh;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hilary_and_jackie